The paper proposes a new algorithm for a multi-objective contextual multi-armed bandit problem, which involves machine learning and decision-making. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The problem also has applications in control systems (cs.SY) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA), which are also possible sub-categories.
